  "title": "Sino-Korean Numbers",
  "objectives": [
    "Count with 일 이 삼 사 오 and beyond",
    "Use Sino numbers for dates, money, and minutes",
    "Read large numbers smoothly"
  ],
  "context": [
    "Korean has two number systems. Sino-Korean numbers (한자어 수) come from Chinese and handle money, minutes, phone numbers, floors, months, and more.",
    "Pattern is regular: 일(1) 이(2) 삼(3) 사(4) 오(5) 육(6) 칠(7) 팔(8) 구(9) 십(10).",
    "Combine tens and hundreds like Lego blocks: 이십(20), 삼십오(35), 백오십(150)."
  ],
  "vocabulary": [
    {"word": "공", "english": "zero (phone numbers)", "romanization": "gong", "type": "number"},
    {"word": "영", "english": "zero", "romanization": "yeong", "type": "number"},
    {"word": "일", "english": "one", "romanization": "il", "type": "number"},
    {"word": "이", "english": "two", "romanization": "i", "type": "number"},
    {"word": "삼", "english": "three", "romanization": "sam", "type": "number"},
    {"word": "사", "english": "four", "romanization": "sa", "type": "number"},
    {"word": "오", "english": "five", "romanization": "o", "type": "number"},
    {"word": "십", "english": "ten", "romanization": "sip", "type": "number"},
    {"word": "백", "english": "hundred", "romanization": "baek", "type": "number"},
    {"word": "천", "english": "thousand", "romanization": "cheon", "type": "number"},
    {"word": "만", "english": "ten thousand", "romanization": "man", "type": "number"}
  ],
  "sentences": [
    {"korean": "오늘은 3월 15일이에요.", "english": "Today is March 15th.", "romanization": "oneureun sam-wol sip-o-il-ieyo."},
    {"korean": "가격이 만 오천 원이에요.", "english": "The price is 15,000 won.", "romanization": "gagyeogi man ocheon won-ieyo."},
    {"korean": "회의가 30분 걸려요.", "english": "The meeting takes 30 minutes.", "romanization": "hoeui-ga samsip bun geollyeoyo."},
    {"korean": "제 번호는 010-9876-5432예요.", "english": "My number is 010-9876-5432.", "romanization": "je beonhoneun gong-il-gong, gu-pal-chil-yuk, o-sa-sam-i-yeyo."},
    {"korean": "십이층에 살아요.", "english": "I live on the 12th floor.", "romanization": "sibi cheunge sarayo."}
